<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Privacy Policy | Wanderlust</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

    <!-- Bootstrap -->
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />

    <style>
      body {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
      }
      .container-box {
        background: white;
        padding: 30px;
        margin-top: 40px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      h1,
      h2 {
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="container-box">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-muted">Last updated: <%= new Date().toDateString() %></p>

        <p>
          Welcome to <strong>Wanderlust</strong>. Your privacy is important to
          us. This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your
          information.
        </p>

        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Name, email, and account details</li>
          <li>Listings you create or interact with</li>
          <li>Usage data like pages visited</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. How We Use Your Data</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>To provide and improve our services</li>
          <li>To personalize your experience</li>
          <li>To communicate updates and support</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. Data Protection</h2>
        <p>
          We use secure technologies and practices to protect your data.
          However, no system is 100% secure.
        </p>

        <h2>4. Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          We use cookies to enhance your browsing experience and analyze
          traffic.
        </p>

        <h2>5. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>
          We may use third-party tools (like maps or authentication services).
        </p>

        <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You can request to access, update, or delete your data anytime.</p>

        <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions, contact us at:
          <strong>support@wanderlust.com</strong>
        </p>

        <a href="/listings" class="btn btn-primary mt-3">Back to Home</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
